      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.XQRMnEeFugGyDUfq]{Steward Officer}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.2zjfszFAX3NdZefF]{Stewards Stalwart}</p>\n<p>You gain one of the following feats as a bonus feat, provided you meet all the prerequisites of the chosen feat: @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.54qpDSqRUsVRWOSZ]{Advanced Melee Weapon Proficiency}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.B45QyyepcPHcjYtr]{Improved Unarmed Strike}, or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.L7RuZ5Mvv7knW70t]{Longarm Proficiency}. If you already have all the listed feats, you can choose a bonus combat feat instead. At 6th level, if you chose Improved Unarmed Strike at 4th level, you gain @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.0Pq35gvSI2JlD682]{Improved Combat Maneuver}. Otherwise, you gain the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.9Us7Eg9cAoq3BcS5]{Weapon Specialization} feat as a bonus feat for the same weapon type to which the bonus feat you gained at 4th level applies.</p>"
